/hooks

Automation hooks run external programs on lifecycle events. Treat hook payloads/logs as potentially sensitive.

Quickstart:
  xcodex hooks init
  xcodex hooks install sdks list
  xcodex hooks install sdks python
  xcodex hooks install samples list
  xcodex hooks install samples external
  xcodex hooks help
  xcodex hooks test external --configured-only
  xcodex hooks list
  xcodex hooks paths

Config: CODEX_HOME/config.toml
Logs: CODEX_HOME/tmp/hooks/logs
Payloads: CODEX_HOME/tmp/hooks/payloads

Docs: docs/xcodex/hooks.md and docs/xcodex/hooks-gallery.md and docs/xcodex/hooks-sdks.md and docs/xcodex/hooks-python-host.md and docs/xcodex/hooks-pyo3.md
